      <title>美国股票期权的散户交易者规模比以往任何时候都大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/retail-traders-are-getting-bigger-than-ever-in-us-stock-options</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通表示，非专业投资者目前在美国期权市场中所占的份额比以往任何时候都要大，他们尤其将资金投入短期押注并青睐科技股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/retail-traders-are-getting-bigger-than-ever-in-us-stock-options</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 20:15:08 GMT</pubDate>
